      <title>Arbor Realty 公布季度业绩后股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/arbor-realty-shares-rise-after-company-posts-quarterly-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公寓大楼贷款机构 Arbor Realty Trust Inc. 的股价周五上涨逾 1%，此前该公司公布了季度业绩，并披露了卖空者所称的不当交易的更多细节。]]></description>
